data.title: Addresses of William Zeckendorf, president of Webb & Knapp, Inc. before New York Society of Security Analysts; July 1, 1953 and July 14, 1953
data.text: Digitized material in this online archive may document imagery or language that reflects racist, ableist, sexist, homophobic, or otherwise offensive and harmful beliefs and actions in history. Hagley Library is engaged in ongoing efforts to address and responsibly present evidence of oppression and injustice in our collections. If you are concerned about the archival material presented here, or want to learn more about our ongoing work, please contact us at research@hagley.org.
